<HL>
   Gulf Resources' Moves to Acquire Assets
   In New Zealand Are Concern for EPA
   ----
   By David Stipp
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/04/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A9A
</SO>
<CO>
   GRE T.GOU FREST
</CO>
